               <p>JOHN BICKERLEY sworn. - I produce a certificate from the clerk of the assize, of the conviction of the prisoner, and of the order to be transported for seven years.</p>
               <p>Q.Were you present at the trial? - A. No, I know nothing but the apprehending him on the <rs id="t18030216-15-cd85" type="crimeDate">2d of February</rs>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18030216-15-off84 t18030216-15-cd85"></join>, in <placeName id="t18030216-15-crimeloc86">Horseshoe-alley, Petticoat-lane</placeName>
